    "body": "This PR moves us off of https://github.com/pre-commit/action to running pre-commit directly. This should avoid the transitive dependency pinning issues from #7536.\r\n\r\nI've also reduced our pin update frequency for `pre-commit` to minor versions since we're getting weekly dependabot updates that aren't necessary. This matches our existing constraints for other ecosystems.",
